values.label: Agriculture
values.comment: Government agency responsible for agriculture and e.g. the inspection of vegetable and animal substances being imported.

values.label: Ammunition
values.comment: Government agency responsible for the safe transport of ammunition.

values.label: Commerce
values.comment: Government agency responsible for commerce both domestic and international.

values.label: Coastguard
values.comment: Government agency responsible for public safety on waterways.

values.label: Food and drug
values.comment: Government agency responsible for the safety on food and drugs.

values.label: Harbour police
values.comment: Police authorities responsible for public safety in the harbour.

values.label: Immigration
values.comment: Government agency responsible for immigration matters.

values.label: Live animals
values.comment: Government agency responsible for the importation of live animals.

values.label: Port authority
values.comment: Government or semi-government body responsible for port operations.

values.label: Public health
values.comment: Government body responsible for public health matters.

values.label: Transportation
values.comment: Government agency responsible for transportation policy and other transportation matters.

values.label: Port state control
values.comment: Government body responsible for the policing of the port.

values.label: Fisheries
values.comment: Government agency responsible for the sustainable harvesting of aquatic organisms.

values.label: Mineral resources
values.comment: Government agency responsible for the sustainable extraction, processing and transportation of mineral resources.

values.label: Environment
values.comment: Government agency responsible for the protection of the environment against destruction or degradation due to natural or human causes.

values.label: Nuclear safety
values.comment: Government agency responsible for protection against harmful radiation arising from radioactive substances.

values.label: Natural Resources
values.comment: Government agency responsible for natural resources such as: energy, minerals, metals, forests.
